## 📖 Overview

**Embedduino** is a **fully custom-designed Arduino-compatible SMD development board**, built around the **ATmega328P-AU** microcontroller.

It is not just a clone — it is a **hardware-engineered platform** integrating:
- Multi-stage power regulation
- Peripheral expansion capability
- Compact PCB layout optimization
- Real-world embedded design practices

> 🎯 هدف: Bridge the gap between *learning Arduino* and *designing real hardware systems*

---

## ✨ Key Features

### 🔹 Core System
- ATmega328P-AU (TQFP Package)
- 16 MHz Crystal Oscillator
- Arduino UNO Compatible Pinout

### 🔹 Power Management
- Dual-stage LDO regulation:
  - **12V → 5V**
  - **5V → 3.3V**
- USB Type-C Power Input
- Barrel Jack (12V) Input
- Power Filtering & Stability Capacitors

### 🔹 Connectivity
- UART Interface (TX/RX)
- Bluetooth Module Support (HC-05 / HC-06)
- ICSP Programming Header

### 🔹 Onboard Peripherals
- RGB LED Indicator
- Status LEDs
- Buzzer Output
- Reset & Enable Push Buttons

### 🔹 Expandability
- Full Digital & Analog Pin Breakout
- Peripheral Interface Section
- Gesture Control Ready Design

---

## 🏗️ System Architecture

```text
        +----------------------+
        |   12V Barrel Input   |
        +----------+-----------+
                   |
                   v
        +----------------------+
        |   12V → 5V LDO       |
        +----------+-----------+
                   |
                   v
        +----------------------+
        |   5V → 3.3V LDO      |
        +----------+-----------+
                   |
        +----------+-----------+
        |                      |
        v                      v
+--------------+      +------------------+
| ATmega328P   |      | Peripherals      |
| (16 MHz)     |      | BT, LEDs, Buzzer |
+--------------+      +------------------+
````

