## 🧪 Applications

* 🤖 Robotics Systems
* 🌐 IoT Devices
* 📡 Wireless Communication Projects
* 🎓 Academic Embedded Labs
* 🎮 Gesture-Control Systems

---

## ⚠️ Limitations

* Linear regulators → thermal inefficiency under load
* External USB-to-Serial required
* No onboard protection ICs (future scope)

---

## 🔮 Roadmap

* [ ] Switching Regulator (Buck Converter)
* [ ] Onboard USB-UART (CH340 / CP2102)
* [ ] ESP32 Variant
* [ ] Compact Version (Nano Form Factor)
* [ ] Hardware Debugging Interface

